README:

1. To Build both Toolchain and Firmware image: 
   1.1 Host Ubuntu 12.04 or higher (Linux kernel 3.2.0) on x86 machine
   1.2 Compiling tool version: gcc 4.6.3 or higher, GNU Make version 3.81

2. Put the package gpl_wr1043ndv4_un.tar.gz to a directory such as /home/TP-LINK, then extract the compressed files.
   $ cd /home/TP-LINK
   $ tar xzvf gpl_wr1043ndv4_un.tar.gz

To Build Firmware image:
   1.1 Go to gpl_wr1043ndv4_un build folder and execute make.
   $ cd /home/TP-LINK/gpl_wr1043ndv4_un/build
   $ make
   will generate the wr1043ndv4_un_(xxx).bin, under gpl_wr1043ndv4_un/images/wr1043ndv4_un folder. 
   xxx refers to flash, up or up_boot, with specific time-stamp and version info.